## Typography Hierarchy

### Font Selection
- **Arabic Support**: GE SS TWO family (Light, Medium, Bold) - for Arabic content
- **English Primary**: Gotham family (Light, Book, Medium, Bold) - digital optimized
- **Current Strangeways**: Maintain for brand consistency while transitioning

### Typography Scale
- **Logo/Heading 1**: 4rem (64px) - National Bonds branding
- **Navigation**: 1.5rem (24px) - Clear, readable menu items
- **Body Large**: 1.25rem (20px) - Main content areas
- **Body Regular**: 1rem (16px) - Standard text
- **Caption**: 0.875rem (14px) - Supporting information

